This paper deals with a method for sequence classification using confidence values, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the discovery of shifting patterns, which is related to data mining (cs.DM) and signal processing (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of time windows, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV).
